==English==

===Etymology===

From the German ''Ersatz'', a replacement; and from the German verb ''ersetzen'', to replace.

===Noun===
'''ersatz'''

# Something made in [[imitation]]; an [[effigy]] or [[substitute]].

===Adjective===
'''ersatz'''

# Made in [[imitation]]; artificial, especially of an inferior quality.

